close_reason: "Implemented validate warning-only semantics: warnings remain visible through has_warnings/warnings, ok only flips false for explicit error-severity findings, diagnostic ID lists default to compact 40-item summaries with --verbose-diagnostics escape hatch, and --strict-exit/--fail-on-warn preserve warning-fail automation."
